<h2>What is it?</h2>
<p>Modation is an extension for Google's Chrome web browser that extends community functionality for <a href="http://soundation.com"><strong>Soundation</strong></a>, an online collaborative music studio. This extension adds a button to the Chrome toolbar for easy access to all notifications on your Soundation account. When you receive a new message or group invitation, a number will appear on the added toolbar button, and a desktop notification will appear on your screen.</p>